description: TENA Maxi Night pads are our longest and most absorbent incontinence pad for night time protection. Designed with extra long length, a wide back & front and side leak guards for heavy absorbency, security and coverage. Suitable for day wear, but is ideal for lie down night protection.Features TENA Triple Protection against leaks, odour and moisture. Rapidly locks fluid deep into the pad, ensuring it doesn't leak out when lying down. BodyFit™ shape contours to the body and side leak guards offer added security.Fresh Odour Control and breathable fabric for long-lasting freshness.Extra long length, a wide back & front and side leak guards for heavy absorbency, security and coverage.Recommended for:Peace of mind for night time protection when lying down When you need extra absorbency and security such as a long car, bus or plane trips
